This software isn't free of use.
you can use code freely from it,
but you have no right to publsh it,
sell it or claim it as your own,

you can freely modify it for you personnal use
or give a copy of your modified software if what you did is of significante importance:

- modified a core game features(modding),
- if you only give the part you modified,
- or if it fix a bug

you cannot give a copy if:

- you introduced a vulnerability
- you injected malware
- you did not change any game features of the software

this license should be included in every copy of this software
this license only cover the initial software unless you include it in you modified software